subject: Basketball (College)
NCAA Basketball Championships (Men)
lead_paragraph: The relentless rebounding of Dustin Hogue, a Yonkers native, is a big reason Iowa State won the Big 12 tournament and is a No. 3 seed in the East Region of the N.C.A.A. tournament.
